dc_title_s: Kaisei Mie-ken gunson meisaizu zen; Kamai Yūjirō.
dc_description_s: Oriented with north to the upper right. Mounted cover title. Title on map: Kaisei Mie-ken gunson meisaizu. Copperplate print. In Japanese. Relief shown by hachures. 4 sheets joined. Includes text on districts, preface and legend. 1 map: col.; 49 x 76 cm., folded in cover 13 x 13 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
